  New upstream version.

*rtorrent-0.2.5 (15 Jun 2005)

  15 Jun 2005; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> rtorrent-0.2.2.ebuild,
  rtorrent-0.2.3.ebuild, rtorrent-0.2.4.ebuild, +rtorrent-0.2.5.ebuild:
